<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說<delay20 />昨天<tag a="110" b="4" />送來的<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個聖誕老人的禮物，
裡面裝的其實是<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是非常可愛的玩具喔！<delay40 />
收下後心裡都變得暖洋洋的～<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕節果然很棒呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能收到聖誕老人的禮物讓我非常開心，<delay20 />
害我昨天情緒High到最高點，<delay8 />
都沒辦法好好睡覺喔～！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而<tag a="110" b="4" />
替我將禮物送過來的事，<delay20 />
也成為了我寶貴回憶的一部分囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的交換禮物真開心呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經打開我送的禮物了嗎？
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那可是我為了<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
精心挑選的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要好好珍惜它喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我心目中的<delay20 /><tag a="90" b="27" />年<delay8 />
平安夜快樂回憶獎的得主<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就決定是和<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
進行的交換禮物了～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，恭喜你！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你明年也要以得獎為目標，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />繼續和我交換禮物喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
我超享受<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的平安夜喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你明明還要忙著幫聖誕老人送禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />卻還是特地來跟我交換禮物，<delay8 />
真的很謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天不光是收到了聖誕老人的禮物，<delay20 />
還拿到了<tag a="110" b="4" />的禮物，<delay8 />
真的是最棒的一天啊～
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而今天的聖誕節，<delay20 />
我打算沉浸在昨天的餘韻中<delay8 />
悠閒地度過喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的平安夜<delay8 />過得如何啊～？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我過得還挺開心的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過說實話，我是很想跟
<tag a="110" b="4" />玩交換禮物的……<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過這份樂趣只能留待明年了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
昨天的平安夜<delay20 />你過得開心嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨天享用了很好吃的蛋糕喔！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />我還另外買了一個蛋糕
來慶祝今天的聖誕節，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我待會就會打開來吃了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>